<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.5">
<l>piṟaṅkiya pēycci mulaicuvait tuṇṭiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuṟaṅkuvāṉ pōlē kiṭantavip piḷḷai</l>
<l>maṟaṅko ḷiraṇiyaṉ mārpaimuṉ kīṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>kuṟaṅku kaḷaivantu kāṇīrē kuvimulai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with round breasts, come and see the thighs</l>
<l>of he who long ago split the chest of the wrathful Hiraṇya,</l>
<l>[of] this child, who sleeps like the one who slept</l>
<l>after eating, sucking the breast of the shining demoness. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
